des:
Everyone likes Star Wars, right? Why not get an awesome Star Wars quote every once in a while? Star Wars Quotes does what it says on the metaphorical box: Gives you Star Wars Quotes!

I made this as a Star Wars fan, and I am not associated with Star Wars, Lucasfilm, or Disney in any way.

May the force be with you.
